Scripts Overview
1. Akamai WAF Detector (akamai_waf_detector.py)
Detects Akamai WAF presence through known signatures

Tests common Akamai endpoints and headers

Identifies WAF block pages and responses

2. Akamai Bypass Tester (akamai_bypass_tester.py)
Tests various WAF bypass techniques:

URL encoding attacks

Unicode normalization

HTTP verb tampering

Header injection

Parameter pollution

Example Results
https://images/results-example.png

Supported Akamai WAF Detection Methods
Response header analysis

Block page fingerprinting

Known endpoint probing

Status code analysis

Content pattern matching

Legal & Ethical Usage
⚠️ Important: This tool is for authorized security testing only.

